@startuml
node "云服务器" {
  artifact "Docker Host" as Host

  frame "Docker Compose" {
    [Nginx] as N #LightBlue
    [Spring Boot App] as App #LightGreen
    [MinIO] as M #Gold
    [MySQL] as DB #Pink
    [Redis] as R #Orange
  }
}

N -left-> App : 反向代理\n(80→8080)
App -down-> M : 9000端口
App -down-> DB : 3306端口
App -down-> R : 6379端口

note top of Host
  部署规范：
  - 所有服务通过docker-compose编排
  - MinIO配置持久化存储卷
  - 启用nginx速率限制
end note
@enduml